- contact an appropriate specialist;
- view official documentation.

Do not combine several unrelated CTAs.

Do not use pressure or false urgency.

Do not imply that the reader must purchase to achieve the article’s basic outcome.

CONTENT UPGRADE

When a lead magnet or content upgrade is included:

- explain what it contains;
- explain who it is for;
- state delivery method;
- state whether marketing communication follows;
- avoid overstating its value.

Do not invent a downloadable resource.

Do not call a short worksheet a complete course or system.

