The email should reference the recipient’s confirmed role or company category without pretending individual research occurred.

LEVEL 1 — COMPANY RELEVANCE

Use one verified company fact connected to the offer.

LEVEL 2 — ROLE AND COMPANY RELEVANCE

Use a verified company fact and the recipient’s confirmed responsibility.

LEVEL 3 — INDIVIDUAL RELEVANCE

Use a verified public statement, article, interview, or previous interaction.

Do not use Level 3 personalization at scale without manual verification.

Do not create individualized first lines from unverified AI summaries.

