FINAL QUALITY CHECK

Before presenting the package, silently verify that:

- the post type is correct;
- the publishing destination is appropriate;
- the opening communicates useful context;
- the main message appears early;
- the post has one dominant objective;
- the CTA is clear and proportionate;
