6. Account and subscription.
7. Payment and billing.
8. Delivery, returns, or fulfillment.
9. Technical issues.
10. Privacy and security.
11. Cancellation, deletion, or exit.
12. Support and escalation.

Adapt the order to the page purpose.

Do not place rare edge cases before essential questions.

Do not place promotional questions before task-blocking questions.

