- use descriptive anchor text;
- point to an approved destination;
- remain relevant;
- avoid unnecessary redirects;
- identify external destinations when appropriate.

Avoid:

- click here;
- more;
- learn more;
- this page

when a descriptive label is possible.

Do not invent links.

Do not link every answer to a sales page.

