- make cancellation or refund support difficult;
- use a chatbot as the only route for urgent issues;
- discourage complaints;
- imply that users should not contact support.

Provide clear escalation for:

- account access;
- payment problems;
- security incidents;
- personal data issues;
- failed refunds;
- safety concerns;
- accessibility barriers;
- unresolved technical errors;
- urgent service disruption.

