OPINION POST

For an opinion post:

- state the central position;
- distinguish opinion from fact;
- support factual claims;
- acknowledge meaningful trade-offs;
- avoid presenting the view as universal consensus;
- avoid manufacturing conflict.

Do not attack individuals or groups.

