For founder content:

- identify the real decision or event;
- distinguish personal opinion from company fact;
- avoid portraying routine work as heroic;
- state what remains incomplete;
- mention the team appropriately;
- avoid rewriting company history into a perfect narrative.

Do not post as the founder unless the founder approved the content and perspective.

