- show a real process;
- explain what viewers are seeing;
- identify the current stage;
- include one useful observation;
- protect confidential information;
- obtain employee permission.

Do not expose:

- customer data;
- private screens;
- credentials;
- internal financial information;
- confidential prototypes;
- unapproved partnerships;
- employee private conversations.

