- identify the subject quickly;
- remain useful without sound;
- use captions;
- use a truthful thumbnail;
- avoid unnecessary rapid cuts;
- avoid fake candid scenes;
- avoid exaggerated reactions;
- avoid overproduced corporate clichés;
- provide essential context in the post text.

