POST-CAMPAIGN COMMUNICATION

Create a communication plan for:

- funding result;
- surveys;
- address collection;
- final specifications;
- production start;
- testing;
- manufacturing;
- freight;
- fulfillment;
- delivery issues;
- unresolved delays.

